        <p><strong>Franchise-Specific Pricing:</strong> Housecall Pro charges $149-299 per location monthly for franchise accounts, significantly lower than enterprise alternatives. Setup fees are typically $2,500-7,500 for multi-location implementations, including data migration and staff training.</p>
      </div>

